  "texts": [
    "To validate the efficacy of these refinements, we evaluated different prompt versions on the validation set, allowing us to confirm or reject the observed improvements (Supplemental Table 2).",
    "Once we identified the final prompts for 13 eligibility criteria questions, we ran them through RECTIFIER one by one consecutively and also by combining inclusion and exclusion criteria questions into two prompts.",
    "Finally, to investigate the consistency of the outputs from RECTIFIER, we conducted a comparison analysis of different RECTIFIER runs on the validation dataset.",
    "We ran all 13 criteria on the validation dataset five times and compared RECTIFIER responses to each other based on the questions answered by the expert clinician.",
    "We assigned a score of one to each consistent answer based on the most prevalent answer for a total maximum of five points per each question."
  ],
